@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "CV Parser" as CVParser
participant "CV Editor" as CVEditor
participant "Screening Question Manager" as ScreeningQuestionManager
participant "Rating Generator" as RatingGenerator
CVParser ->> CVEditor : Parse CV and send data
CVEditor -> ScreeningQuestionManager : Submit edited CV for screening
ScreeningQuestionManager ->> RatingGenerator : Send screening questions and CV data
CVParser ->> RatingGenerator : Send raw CV data for rating
RatingGenerator -> CVEditor : Notify of updated rating
RatingGenerator -> ScreeningQuestionManager : Notify of updated rating
@enduml